A common interface for color conversion for GPU drivers.

WHAT IT DOES?
=============
The libgpu_aux.so provide a interface for GPU drivers to support 
MTK's color format, such as NV12, or other MTK PRIVATE FORMAT.

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
It needs the following library from MTK:
1.  libdpframework.so

HOW TO USE IT?
==============
